{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Convenience function to connect to the [Cancellable](\/\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable\/oncancelled(flags:handler:)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"signal. Also handles the race condition that may happen"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if the cancellable is cancelled right before connecting."}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"connect(callback:data:dataDestroyFunc:)","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"connect","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"callback","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gclosure.h@T@GCallback","text":"GCallback","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"dataDestroyFunc"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GDestroyNotify"},{"text":"?) -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO19CancellableProtocolPAAE7connect8callback4data0F11DestroyFuncSiyyXCSg_SvSgyAIXCSgtF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"connect","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"callback"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GCallback","preciseIdentifier":"c:gclosure.h@T@GCallback"},{"text":"?, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"data","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"gpointer","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"text":"? = nil, ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dataDestroyFunc","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@GDestroyNotify","text":"GDestroyNotify"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil) -> "},{"text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"callback","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is called exactly once each time "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is cancelled,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"either directly at the time of the connect if "},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is already"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cancelled, or when "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is cancelled in some thread."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In case the cancellable is reset via [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.reset"},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"then the callback can be called again if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is cancelled and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"if it had not been previously cancelled at the time"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Cancellable.connect","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] was called (e.g. if the connection actually"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"took place, returning a non-zero value).","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"dataDestroyFunc","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be called when the handler is","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"disconnected, or immediately if the cancellable is already","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"cancelled."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See [Cancellable](\/\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable\/oncancelled(flags:handler:) for details on how to use this."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Since GLib 2.40, the lock protecting ","type":"text"},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is not held when"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"callback","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is invoked. This lifts a restriction in place for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"earlier GLib versions which now makes it easier to write cleanup","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"code that unconditionally invokes e.g. [method"},{"code":"Gio.Cancellable.cancel","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note that since 2.82 GLib still holds a lock during the callback but it’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"designed in a way that most of the [class","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Cancellable","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] methods can be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"called, including [method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.cancel"},{"type":"text","text":"] or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"GObject.Object.unref","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"There are still some methods that will deadlock (by design) when","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called from the [signal[Cancellable](\/\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable\/oncancelled(flags:handler:)] callbacks:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.connect"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.disconnect"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Cancellable.reset","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.Cancellable.make_pollfd","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Cancellable.release_fd","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/cancellableref\/connect(callback:data:datadestroyfunc:)"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef\/CancellableProtocol-Implementations"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef\/connect(callback:data:dataDestroyFunc:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/Cancellable":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Cancellable"}],"title":"Cancellable","type":"topic","abstract":[{"code":"GCancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" allows operations to be cancelled.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Cancellable","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Cancellable","url":"\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/CancellableRef/connect(callback:data:dataDestroyFunc:)":{"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/